title: North vs South divide in Rugby World Cup quarterfinals
text:
> Sports North vs South divide in Rugby World Cup quarterfinals France's Bernard Le Roux, centre, captain Thierry Dusautoir, left, and Morgan Parra leave the field after the Rugby World Cup Pool D match between France and Ireland at the Millennium Stadium in Cardiff, Wales, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. Ireland won the match 24-9. (AP Photo/Alastair Grant)
